Kenya Breweries Limited recently launched a new and exciting pop culture DJs competition dubbed the Smirnoff Battle of the Beats. The 12-week competition will see up and coming DJ prospects meet and battle it out on the decks each week to find the next big Kenyan entertainer. Present were top-notch DJs who showcased their skills, namely DJ Hypnotic, DJ Pierra, DJ Xclusive and the only DJ Mellow. Also present were KBL premium spirits brand manager Wanjiku Njonjo, shopper manager Judy Natichi and legendary DJs Pinye, Stylez and Spoonie, who came to show their support for the craft.